  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.3.0-alpha03\" data-text=\"Version 1.3.0-alpha03\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.3.0-alpha03</h3>\n<p>October 30, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.wear.protolayout:protolayout-*:1.3.0-alpha03</code> is released. Version 1.3.0-alpha03 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/b8a68b0896897fa158508d73a31998a26161d9a7..ccd90a76bd7c4acf4f4f01eca76350e383bc441e/wear/protolayout\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>New Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">LayoutElementAssertionsProvider</code>, <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">LayoutElementAssertion</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">LayoutElementMatcher</code> to the testing library (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Id11101d0217410f4ab0ddfb571d7624a9fcf0e43\">Id1110</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
